{"tid":1780372,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"【笑出聲】《哪吒：變形金剛》預告首曝光 大陸網民劣評「變形人吒」","createTime":"2019-12-12T10:08:55.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-13T01:44:44.000Z","uid":141151,"like":9,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":26,"replies":[{"pid":"f7afc3a3a487a3954a07a1a75acafbd9a6983320","tid":1780372,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-12T10:08:55.000Z","msg":"【笑出聲】《哪吒：變形金剛》預告首曝光 大陸網民劣評「變形人吒」<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.entertainment.appledaily.com/enews/realtime/article/20191211/60366722\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.entertainment.appledaily.com%2Fenews%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20191211%2F60366722&d=Vh0AUGqI%2BhuKY3uG7C8FcxVENBC9VnKGSHAjWoGsWeM%3D&h=e475bdcc\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.entertainment.appledaily.com%2Fenews%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20191211%2F60366722&h=1e06120b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.entertainment.appledaily.com/enews/realtime/article/20191211/60366722</a><br />\n<br />\n今年5月《變形金剛》在官方網站中，公佈母公司孩之寶集團CEO Brian Goldner與中央電視台合作，推出變形金剛與哪吒Crossover動畫。<br />\n<br />\n事隔半年，萬眾期待嘅《哪吒：變形金剛》預告片今日終於有得睇，雖然只有短短分半鐘，但大陸網民就似乎頂唔順呢個「當哪吒遇上變形金剛」嘅劇情，一致劣評。<br />\n<br />\n據資料顯示，今次呢套《哪吒：變形金剛》係講述<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">「正義勇敢的哪吒和小伙伴與變形金剛攜手，共同戰勝邪惡，並得到變形金剛欽佩</span></span></strong>」嘅故事。預告片最初先有哪吒攞住個金剛圈、踩住風火輪狂擺pose，之後鏡頭一轉，就去到變形金剛與反派對戰，同時被譽為「正義勇敢」化身嘅哪吒，就以「美少女戰士」經典變身畫面出場，心口突然出現蓮花的哪吒，猶如「變身鏡盒」，全身變出紅金色盔甲，然後再一次狂擺pose。「變形人吒」套盔甲靚唔靚真係見仁見智，不過用色就好有中國特色，又紅又金又黃咁喇！但唔明嘅係，哪吒點解着盔甲，依然係堅持露出5隻腳趾，睇嚟就算變身，哪吒都堅持赤腳。<br />\n<br />\n除了有「人吒」變身片段，當然亦會有佢、柯柏文及大黃蜂等合作場面，又同麥加登激烈打鬥場面，配合《變形金剛》劇情。將中國神話人物跟唔同風格嘅機械人結合變成動畫，就惹嚟大陸網民一致劣評，紛紛留言「廣電總局這時候怎麼不說破壞歷史文化毒害未成年歷史觀」、「90後的童年快被毀」、「頭號毀童年系列，一毀毀兩個IP，哪吒頭金剛身，非常具有喜感」、「求求他們不要浪費電影資源好嗎」等，另有哪吒fans表示兩者合作覺得莫名其妙：「我吒吒都三頭六臂了，還需要這沙X裝備」、「我覺得這是一種侮辱，把神話人物變成這樣」。<br />\n<br />\n預告片<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/UIB5Mk90t2w\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FUIB5Mk90t2w&d=Vh0AUGqI%2BhuKY3uG7C8FcxVENBC9VnKGSHAjWoGsWeM%3D&h=669a4f7c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/UIB5Mk90t2w</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Hjgau2R.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FHjgau2R.jpg&h=d9c67f2b&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/12/12/180833_acd5144db597d33acff33c595d37432f.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F12%2F12%2F180833_acd5144db597d33acff33c595d37432f.jpeg&h=46ea778a&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/12/12/180834_56938b73f1e477ab2106765a850024dd.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F12%2F12%2F180834_56938b73f1e477ab2106765a850024dd.jpeg&h=fa01ba34&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/12/12/180836_d86a61389d41b2afffcc37ba7eaacbc3.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F12%2F12%2F180836_d86a61389d41b2afffcc37ba7eaacbc3.jpeg&h=27c0112a&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/12/12/180837_93a1cf3b3866183050c9e9b7093f1c88.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F12%2F12%2F180837_93a1cf3b3866183050c9e9b7093f1c88.jpeg&h=aa80f26c&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/12/12/180838_2309e2d0dea89f07e661bd8e77688914.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F12%2F12%2F180838_2309e2d0dea89f07e661bd8e77688914.jpeg&h=cf3fb3b5&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/12/12/180839_a10c99fd02ffaa6633888e29856f31b0.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F12%2F12%2F180839_a10c99fd02ffaa6633888e29856f31b0.jpeg&h=2ddd02de&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"ht